headline: Expecting the longest run of earnings growth in the energy sector: Jefferies' Julien Dumoulin-Smith
summary: Julien Dumoulin-Smith, Jefferies analyst, joins 'Power Lunch' to discuss how AI will impact the energy sector, if utilities are given money back to customers and much more.
